  "byline": null,
  "publishedAt": null,
  "contentHtml": "<figure><a href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/%24s_!w6Is!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5de5d442-0449-4f37-a82b-7e09457b3074_2756x748.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/%24s_!w6Is!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5de5d442-0449-4f37-a82b-7e09457b3074_2756x748.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"395\" data-size=\"normal\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n\n\n</a></figure>\n<p>In this space on Saturdays, I <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/t/roundup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">do a weekly round-up</a> of sorts: Sifting through what I wrote that you might have missed during the week, what I’ve been reading and watching myself, and some other fun things that have been going on.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/subscribe?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p>\n<hr>\n<h4>📝 What I did this week</h4>\n<p><em>Here are the things I wrote or podcasted about during the previous week, sorted in descending order by quality, popularity and/or current relevance.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><strong>⚾ <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/garret-anderson-was-the-angels-constant\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Garret Anderson Was the Angels’ Constant</a></strong> - Last week’s sad news, that the longtime Angels outfielder <a href=\"https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/48513802/long-angels-outfielder-garret-anderson-dies-53\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">had passed away at 53</a>, made me recall just what a baseball fixture he was in an era where Anaheim evolved from an also-ran to a perennial contender and champion.</p></li>\n<li>\n<p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/the-pistons-dominated-one-nba-now\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Pistons Dominated One NBA. Now They Have to Survive the Other.</a></strong> - Detroit won 60 games during the regular season, but they went into the playoffs as disrespected as just about any No. 1 seed this century… then proceeded to live down to their doubters’ expectations in Game 1 against Orlando. Now tied 1-1, they have to keep fighting to prove they belong among the top contenders.</p>\n<ul><li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://news.polymarket.com/p/the-nba-playoffs-are-a-different\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The NBA Playoffs Are a Different Sport</a></strong> - Relatedly, I wrote a guest post for  about how the NBA playoffs are breaking away from the regular season more and more in recent years — in style, but also especially in the relationship between how the former predicts the latter.</p></li></ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>⚾ <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/the-nl-east-is-reverting-to-historical\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The NL East Is Reverting to Historical Form</a></strong> - History is repeating in this season’s NL East, where the Atlanta Braves are maintaining a steady winning pace while their supposed biggest rivals — the Mets and Phillies — are battling to see who can have the longest losing streak. </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🏒 <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/dont-tell-buffalo-and-montreal-the\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Don’t Tell Buffalo and Montreal the NHL Playoffs Aren’t Any Place For Young Teams</a></strong> - Despite the conventional wisdom about experience winning in the playoffs, two of the three youngest teams in the league — the Sabres and Canadiens — also <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/2025-26-nhl-elo-ratings-and-win-projections\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">have decent shots at meeting next round</a> with a conference final berth on the line.</p></li>\n<li>\n<p>🏁 <strong><a href=\"https://www.nascar.com/news-media/2026/04/23/tyler-reddick-wont-stop-winning-so-lets-update-his-season-projection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tyler Reddick won’t stop winning — so let’s update his season projection</a></strong> - The winningest driver in  this season claimed another victory last week, so I updated <a href=\"https://www.nascar.com/news-media/2026/03/26/how-many-races-will-tyler-reddick-win-this-season/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">my previous story</a> on how many races he might end up winning, while also introducing a method of estimating <a href=\"https://www.driveraverages.com/drvavg/nascar-driverratings.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Driver Ratings</a> for years prior to 2005. </p>\n<div class=\"reader-datawrapper\"><a href=\"https://datawrapper.dwcdn.net/FO7jL/2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c33cd78e-aa94-42a5-88d7-adcf954b32db_1220x2064.png\" alt=\"The most dominant Driver Rating seasons\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></a><p>The most dominant Driver Rating seasons</p></div>\n<ul><li><p>🏁🎙️ <strong><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/4EP1bTE1M9u6RkRMTjz9fB?si=q09nN4tFT8O_bASqS5QKvg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Podracing: Machine Learnin’</a></strong> - In this week’s episode of , <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tyler-lauletta-b0399667/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> Lauletta</a> and I talked about — what else? — Reddick’s latest (and arguably wildest) win, plus we unpacked my story on the most dominant seasons, applied my new method to historical Talladega races, and made our betting and one-and-done picks for the upcoming weekend in Alabama.</p></li></ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/after-fernando-mendoza-then-what\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">After Fernando Mendoza, Then What?</a></strong> - One of the <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/195257975/find-the-edge\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">big questions</a> ahead of this year’s NFL Draft was around the quarterback position — would Mendoza be the lone QB in Round 1? Would Ty Simpson go next, and when? I looked at the history of drafts that did and didn’t have huge gaps between QB1 and QB2, and what that tends to mean. (Which the L.A. Rams apparently decided means <a href=\"https://substack.com/@neilpaine/note/c-248449693\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">they think Simpson was better than everyone else thought</a>!)</p></li>\n<li><p>🏒 <strong><a href=\"https://www.espn.com/nhl/story/_/id/48523076/2026-nhl-playoffs-stanley-cup-rankings-top-players-mackinnon-mcdavid-crosby-kucherov\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ranking the top 50 players in the 2026 Stanley Cup playoffs</a></strong> - As the playoffs were getting underway, I used a multi-year weighted average of my <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/2025-26-nhl-goals-above-replacement-leaderboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Goals Above Replacement</a> metric to rate the most productive players on postseason rosters this year.</p></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>📊 Chart(s) of the week:</h4>\n<p>Here were my favorite items of the week from <em><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/scoreboard-newsletter-archives\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Scoreboard</a></strong></em>, my daily newsletter for <a href=\"https://sherwood.news/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sherwood News</a>… </p>\n<p><strong>🏈 </strong><em><strong>On players <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/195367026/chart-of-the-day\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">whose NFL Draft positioning rose or fell</a> vs. expected…</strong></em></p>\n<div class=\"reader-datawrapper\"><a href=\"https://datawrapper.dwcdn.net/gCAql/2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1183b243-18ed-4d8b-81ac-7f2a54d34ef8_1220x1702.png\" alt=\"Who rose or fell in Round 1?\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></a><p>Who rose or fell in Round 1?</p></div>\n<p><strong>⚽ </strong><em><strong>On the <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/194938860/find-the-edge\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">suddenly tight EPL race</a> between Arsenal and Man City…</strong></em></p>\n<div class=\"reader-datawrapper\"><a href=\"https://datawrapper.dwcdn.net/DEtYL/1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/aee76a42-e903-46cb-8d15-9843fd710d4e_1220x1000.png\" alt=\"City has caught up to Arsenal in a hurry\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></a><p>City has caught up to Arsenal in a hurry</p></div>\n<p><strong>⚾ </strong><em><strong>On the <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/195257975/chart-of-the-day\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">divergent paths of NL East teams</a>…</strong></em></p>\n<div class=\"reader-datawrapper\"><a href=\"https://datawrapper.dwcdn.net/weXup/2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d7ca7e4a-21e7-4061-97ac-c97697ebc678_1220x1050.png\" alt=\"The NL East is diverging\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></a><p>The NL East is diverging</p></div>\n<p><em>Subscribe to <strong>Scoreboard</strong> by <strong><a href=\"https://join.sherwood.news/scoreboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">clicking here</a></strong>!</em></p>\n<h4>👀 Some interesting things I read/watched this week</h4>\n<p><em>A collection of articles (with a heavy focus on my fellow Substackers), videos and other media that I enjoyed and/or found thought-provoking over the past week. I don’t always 100% agree with or endorse what’s linked here… but that’s also sort of the point.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://club.sportico.com/p/nfl-draft-2026-data-age-analysis-giants-picks-prospects-big-board\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The NFL Draft is Getting Older. No One Told the Giants</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://blessyourchart.substack.com/p/184-the-nfl-draft-and-the-portal?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1185822&amp;post_id=195061493&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The NFL Draft and the Portal Problem</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://miketanier.substack.com/p/fernando-mendoza-system-qb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fernando Mendoza, System QB</a></strong> and <strong><a href=\"https://miketanier.substack.com/p/such-small-portions-ty-simpson-and?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=2228630&amp;post_id=193790633&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Such Small Portions: Ty Simpson and the Perils of Scouting Overconfidence</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://fancystats.substack.com/p/the-biggest-mistakes-bettors-make?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=7912922&amp;post_id=191255971&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The biggest mistakes bettors make with NFL win totals — and why it costs them money</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🏈 <a href=\"https://www.coachingfootballinsights.com/p/the-football-route-tree-every-route?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=2146974&amp;post_id=194633827&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Football Route Tree: Every Route Explained</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://www.golongtd.com/p/is-the-time-now-for-the-new-york?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=222258&amp;post_id=194903793&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Is the time NOW for the New York Giants? A chat with Joe Praino…</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🏈 <a href=\"https://cfbnumbers.substack.com/p/its-clustering-time-2026-nfl-draft?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=273098&amp;post_id=194944833&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Its Clustering Time! 2026 NFL Draft QB Cluster Analysis</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🏈 <a href=\"https://links.e1.nytimes.com/s/vb/OtUIH9nmEtKecGIzbdvcPfOiVMJ_xtJ9SdZNfGwd_H-bb1UeNjIvmkFdgix78-GMgp01MwAMrDQN6ZZiXmAj38smo3GdEepS7az1vQtqY3l-dv3ViLmvjdz-tJALV-8GPDrJhkil_sc7UB6u/IpJrv7Nlk1nMbt8EFGg83DD7jJwrwhnl/20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Yet another transfer goes No. 1 </a></strong>by <a href=\"https://links.e1.nytimes.com/a/sc/QUP3votzFfpxjEE3eCgdhr0Q9vgw5FTwy2g59rg-WqcsdX6SYiK16-RuBFiOTGokgfieD8dypHOEDoLBCxqg9GXOZd1pil-gsI6ubguzPaH1bKhs0bLbgB0SX5IVmwPl_5PtNxPOUayx4PhYzic_JYf76PtGJ1vreDe1YOiAhYCe1PqlMh3Z-uyT-8EosMrRu9EeiNmU_2CndSSmKC74ndxglB2_p3RfJw91bKaVfo7KVb45Fhh3rg2-S6uibCmxIGzLCZMnSANu1ijy79ErydBqCQM_R97Tb-FUbP2ejfbxrymJytNqJ8zGmHf4297ZHVfDokSv44lRcpzy5jnGt5ReVSv5werIgS4HS2I6I-b0X7Kz6c6LCZKesNOnj6dQor2vPHTgJPPW0R4/4OxIp_bT5gHwig0KeIQY8FkuyQO65A2J/20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Jason Kirk</a></p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://irisketball.substack.com/p/games-about-a-bucket?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=6839761&amp;post_id=195363020&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">game’s about a bucket* or: dyson daniels and the misunderstood definition of offensive value</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://www.houseofstrauss.com/p/nielsens-magic-trick-and-the-nbas?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=446127&amp;post_id=195229181&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=false&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nielsen’s Magic Trick and the NBA’s Same Old Story</a></strong> and <strong><a href=\"https://www.houseofstrauss.com/p/whats-with-you-people-and-the-oklahoma?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=446127&amp;post_id=195023857&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=false&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">What’s With You People and the Oklahoma City Thunder? The Thunder Are Breaking Basketball (Legally)</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://www.noceilingsnba.com/p/2026-nba-playoffs-top-young-player?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=536361&amp;post_id=194430939&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2026 NBA Playoffs: Top Young Player To Watch On Each Playoff Team</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://chartinghoops.substack.com/p/the-value-of-losing?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=4074575&amp;post_id=194660089&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Value of Losing: On the Spurs, Pistons, and Playoff Experience</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://jdbcollegehoops.substack.com/p/the-ten-best-games-i-watched-this?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=6999004&amp;post_id=194643648&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Ten Best Games I Watched This Season</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://omgnewsletter.substack.com/p/remember-the-1998-99-portland-trail?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=506874&amp;post_id=195178189&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Remember the 1998-99 Portland Trail Blazers? // This is one of the best forgotten teams.</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://edwithsports.substack.com/p/not-all-rich-mlb-ballclubs-are-created?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=2391764&amp;post_id=194834132&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Not All Rich MLB Ballclubs are Created Equal</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾<strong> <a href=\"https://ritmica1.substack.com/p/is-sandy-alcantara-back?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=5688290&amp;post_id=194947755&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=false&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Is Sandy Alcántara Back? How the last old school Cy Young campaign created expectations that might someday be fulfilled</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://dougglanville.substack.com/p/jackie-robinson-more-than-first?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=820944&amp;post_id=194656388&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Jackie Robinson: More Than First</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>⚾ <a href=\"https://baseballspreadsheets.substack.com/p/garrett-mitchell-is-having-a-silly?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=6153906&amp;post_id=194803555&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Garrett Mitchell is Having a Silly Season: Look at his BABIP. Look at his strikeout rate.</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://michaelcecchini.substack.com/p/shock-and-aww-shucks?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=2245735&amp;post_id=195195440&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Shock and Aww, Shucks: Pitcher Slugging Fortunes and In-Zone Whiff Misfortunes</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾▶️ <strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4e6l9NTzkg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Do players-only meetings actually matter?</a></strong> by <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@FoolishBailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Foolish Bailey</a></p></li>\n<li><p><strong>⛳ <a href=\"https://thescoringletter.substack.com/p/the-data-says-hit-driver-heres-when?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=6004725&amp;post_id=194530292&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Data Says Hit Driver. Here’s When the Data is Wrong.</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏁 <strong><a href=\"https://motorsportsbeat.substack.com/p/f1-shakes-things-up?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1004156&amp;post_id=195349201&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">F1 Shakes Things Up: The series is making some rule changes ahead of its return to action next month in Miami.</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🔮 <strong><a href=\"https://news.polymarket.com/p/copycat?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=2722650&amp;post_id=195365650&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=false&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">COPYCAT // Here are the 10 most copied Polymarket wallets</a></strong> by  and  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🐎</strong>▶️<strong> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8xXqE0ZiZHw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kentucky Derby qualification details with Steve Kornacki</a></strong> by <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@NBCSports\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NBC Sports</a></p></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>▶️ <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/my-old-games-lists\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Old YouTube Race Game</a> of the Week</h4>\n<p>1988 Winston 500 From Talladega Superspeedway</p>\n<h4>🎵 Music to Play Us Out</h4>\n<p>Roberta Flack And Donny Hathaway - “Where Is The Love”</p>\n<p><em><strong>Filed under:</strong></em> <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/t/roundup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Weekly Round-up</a></p>\n<p>Neil’s Substack is a reader-supported publication. To receive new posts and support my work, consider becoming a free or paid subscriber.</p>",
